                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>\n                <date>June 17<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 5614</date>\n                <add>?</add>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <add>שלום רב וברכה ישפיהו ה' לאיש חיל, היוצא במערכות מלחמות ה', ורבים השיב מעון,\n                    ומתלהב לבם לאמונת אבותינו</add>\n            </p>\n            <p>Rev. Sir!</p>\n            <p>A friend of mine, to whom I <sic>recommanded</sic> Your<lb/> valuable Periodical, the\n                Occt, requests that I shall<lb/> beseech your Hon. to forward to his Address\n                the<lb/> first No of the <sic>comming</sic> monthly Magazine and continue<lb/> to do\n                so successively. He is likewise desirous to<lb/> obtain of the same\n                    <sic>Magazin</sic> the Numbers of the<lb/> past <hi rend=\"underline\">two\n                    years</hi>, neatly Bound <hi rend=\"underline\">in one Volume</hi>,<lb/> wishing,\n                that you might have it in <sic>readness</sic>, for<lb/> the next month, when he\n                anticipates having the<lb/> pleasure of <sic>caling</sic> with you and to settle the\n                    <sic>accont</sic>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">By the same opportunity, I will feel obliged,<lb/> if you will hand\n                him the Papers, containing Certificates<lb/> and Diploma, of mine, send you some\n                time since with an<lb/> Article written <sic>intented</sic> as a reply to the\n                    <persName>Rev I. Rosenfeld</persName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Your leading Art. against progressive Reform<lb/> in the\n                    <date>June</date> No has greatly pleased our friends here, and<lb/> demands our\n                respectful thanks, while the strictures<lb/> against <persName>I. Wise</persName>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">D. D.</hi> in Page 148. has paralyzed even some<lb/> of his\n                best friends—such weapons so powerful and</p>\n            <p rend=\"The following is written sideways in the left margin.\"/>\n            <p>V# <persName>Mr N. Moses</persName>,</p>\n            <p>care of <persName>Hyman Moses &amp; Co.</persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Cincinnati <sic>ohio</sic></placeName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3w669v67/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
